<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Pixel Project Website</title>

  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');

    :root {
      --bg: #070816;
      --card: #111827;
      --cyan: #00eaff;
      --pink: #ff3df2;
      --yellow: #ffd93d;
      --green: #39ff88;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --black: #000000;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(0,234,255,0.18), transparent 35%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(255,61,242,0.18), transparent 35%),
        var(--bg);
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      animation: bg-flicker 3s infinite;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 0px,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px,
        transparent 2px,
        transparent 4px
      );
      z-index: 9999;
      animation: scanline 2s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes scanline {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.16; }
      50% { opacity: 0.07; }
    }

    @keyframes bg-flicker {
      0%, 100% { filter: brightness(1); }
      50% { filter: brightness(1.08); }
    }

    .pixel-border {
      border: 4px solid var(--white);
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 4px var(--black),
        8px 8px 0 var(--black),
        0 0 24px var(--cyan);
    }

    .navbar {
      width: calc(100% - 40px);
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 18px 28px;
      background: rgba(8, 11, 22, 0.95);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .logo {
      font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
      color: var(--yellow);
      font-size: 16px;
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--yellow);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover,
    .nav-links a.active {
      color: var(--cyan);
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--cyan);
    }

    .hero {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 70px auto 40px;
      padding: 40px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
      font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 52px);
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: var(--yellow);
      text-shadow:
        0 0 10px var(--yellow),
        4px 4px 0 var(--black);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 750px;
      margin: auto;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #d6e4ff;
    }

    .section {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 24px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .prop-card {
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 26px;
      min-height: 250px;
      transition: 0.25s;
      position: relative;
    }

    .prop-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 10px;
      border: 2px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .prop-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 4px var(--black),
        10px 10px 0 var(--black),
        0 0 28px var(--pink);
    }

    .prop-card h2 {
      font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--green);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--green);
    }

    .prop-card p {
      color: #dbeafe;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .pixel-btn {
      font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
      font-size: 11px;
      background: var(--yellow);
      color: #111;
      border: 4px solid white;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow:
        0 6px 0 #9b6b00,
        0 0 16px rgba(255, 217, 61, 0.9);
      transition: 0.1s;
    }

    .pixel-btn:hover {
      filter: brightness(1.15);
    }

    .pixel-btn:active {
      transform: translateY(6px);
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 #9b6b00,
        0 0 22px rgba(255, 217, 61, 1);
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 650px) {
      .navbar {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .nav-links {
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .hero {
        margin-top: 35px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <nav class="navbar pixel-border">
    <div class="logo">UMS QUEST</div>

    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#" class="active">HOME</a>
      <a href="#">TEAM</a>
      <a href="#">PROJECT</a>
      <a href="#">CONTACT</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>PIXEL ADVENTURE PROJECT</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to our creative project website. This page uses a retro pixel-art style,
      CRT scanline effect, neon glow, and 3D pixel buttons to make the UI look more
      gempak and game-like.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">

    <div class="prop-card pixel-border">
      <h2>ABOUT TEAM</h2>
      <p>
        Put your team introduction here. You can write member names, roles,
        and what each person contributed to the project.
      </p>
      <button class="pixel-btn">VIEW TEAM</button>
    </div>

    <div class="prop-card pixel-border">
      <h2>ABOUT PROJECT</h2>
      <p>
        Explain your project idea, objective, problem statement, and why this
        project is useful or creative.
      </p>
      <button class="pixel-btn">EXPLORE</button>
    </div>

    <div class="prop-card pixel-border">
      <h2>UMS ODEC</h2>
      <p>
        Add information about ODEC, beach theme, environment, or how it connects
        to your project concept.
      </p>
      <button class="pixel-btn">START</button>
    </div>

  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    © 2026 UMS Quest Project | Pixel Art Theme
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
